title: Sheila E. - Romance 1600
description:
Romance 1600 is the second album from singer/drummer/percussionist Sheila E.. The only track that Prince co-wrote and co-produced with Sheila is "A Love Bizarre", which became a major hit and finds the two of them performing a vocal duet. Prince&#039;s influence is strong throughout the album.
